{"tid":780143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快速支付系統下月生效 銀行發修訂戶口章則","createTime":"2018-08-15T03:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T16:18:55.000Z","uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e4d0c2817f1a0d530a46d391318a4b22a4fe79e4","tid":780143,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T03:10:18.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】因應金管局將於下個月推出快速支付系統，銀行開始向客戶發出通知修訂戶口章則，匯豐及恒生（0011）分別向客戶發出通知，有關修訂將於9月17日起生效。早前市傳快速支付系統將於9月17日推出，修訂生效日期進一步印證相關傳聞。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n匯豐新增修訂條款中，包括新增有關使用二維碼（QR Code）服務、客戶應該知悉的安全問題以及銀行責任及其責任限制的具體條文。據悉，業界在二維碼的共通標準上已有共識，以配合快速支付系統的使用。其他修訂包括：使用該系統提供服務時，客戶個人資料如何被收集、使用、處理及轉移；列出銀行不會負責的損失類型等具體條文。<br />\n<br />\n快速支付系統是金管局總裁陳德霖在去年9月宣布，推動香港智慧銀行的7項措施之一，用於個人對個人和商戶付款，每日24小時轉帳資金。客戶只需要使用手提電話號碼或一個由快速支付系統產生獨有的系統識別碼連結帳戶，其他付款人毋須知道銀行帳戶詳細資料，亦可轉帳。"},{"pid":"6e21e704ee9f364a55dd349a4f078659f6166ca0","tid":780143,"uid":31098,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"「系統」係「啟用」或者「推出」，舐共（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） 嘅就會用「開通」、「出台」。<br />\n<br />\n用「生效」-- 明報係咪中文拎 F 都可以做記者/編輯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9564ca3819b58931170cb9da3b1bfcaf0457d0","tid":780143,"uid":144626,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"呢d垃圾支那寶<br />\n阻撚住人買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f11c012cb4baa8d4bd0f6ab83a4e87632287c7c","tid":780143,"uid":41308,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7f9564ca3819b58931170cb9da3b1bfcaf0457d0","tid":780143,"uid":144626,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"呢d垃圾支那寶<br />\n阻撚住人買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"支那寶真係好Q慢<br />\n<br />\n不過今次金管局要求用EMV Standard wor, VISA有份, 要所有QR code payment要行EMV standard, 要求全部互相通用<br />\n<br />\n支那寶唔收舖頭Service Charge, 一於係支那寶商戶用VISA既QR code俾錢，VISA自然會問支那寶擺錢。到時支那寶俾VISA手續費俾窮佢，但支那寶又出賣唔到你既資料，支那寶睇下到時點生存。"},{"pid":"f1998edef84f1ba5734c4d9f2625ad5fd48756e5","tid":780143,"uid":41622,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"應該唔關支那寶事<br />\n呢個係CHATS嘅進階版<br />\n<br />\n- 免費跨行轉帳<br />\n- 24 X 7 即時到帳<br />\n- 只可轉 HKD / CNY<br />\n- 有對方 手機number / email address / 系統產生嘅username / QR code 就畀到錢<br />\n- 可以set定金額, 整個QR code出嚟畀人找數<br />\n<br />\n個人嚟講幾期待 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f029693d48aac6f1a5321671a364a2a29cf07a75","tid":780143,"uid":27688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f1998edef84f1ba5734c4d9f2625ad5fd48756e5","tid":780143,"uid":41622,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"應該唔關支那寶事<br />\n呢個係CHATS嘅進階版<br />\n<br />\n- 免費跨行轉帳<br />\n- 24 X 7 即時到帳<br />\n- 只可轉 HKD / CNY<br />\n- 有對方 手機number / email address / 系統產生嘅username / QR code 就畀到錢<br />\n- 可以set定金額, 整個QR code出嚟畀人找數<br />\n<br />\n個人嚟講幾期待 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"可惜只有2種貨幣....<br />\n其他Major currencies有咩仲好"},{"pid":"5b36f5a96fa3f154cb86be7b3374c603f6faef45","tid":780143,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"FPS 唔使比手續費咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b852f4bb8fb621a5db