:{"pid":"6e21e704ee9f364a55dd349a4f078659f6166ca0","tid":780143,"uid":31098,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"「系統」係「啟用」或者「推出」，舐共（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） 嘅就會用「開通」、「出台」。<br />\n<br />\n用「生效」-- 明報係咪中文拎 F 都可以做記者/編輯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:40:19.000Z","msg":"「繳費」都變咗「支付」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baae911e5a0c0df197dea9137637b2272fa84126","tid":780143,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"金管局新增銀通及易辦事為指定零售支付系統<br />\n<br />\n金管局宣布，金融管理專員根據《支付系統及儲值支付工具條例》，指定由銀通及易辦事營運的相關零售支付系統。<br />\n<br />\n作為指定零售支付系統，可以傳送支付訊息及相關數據以便利支付交易的處理、授權、結算及交收支付交易、提供支付解決方案以處理不同支付模式所產生的支付交易等。<br />\n<br />\n現時指定的零售支付系統亦包括Visa、Mastercard、銀聯國際、美國運通。"},{"pid":"5431f35c0b6b4e978fdc55f4fabed87c8712c342","tid":780143,"uid":37524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e24fb3d4875f1f5b12961b7cfc13caba7dd0b7d8","tid":780143,"uid":64884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e21e704ee9f364a55dd349a4f078659f6166ca0","tid":780143,"uid":31098,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"「系統」係「啟用」或者「推出」，舐共（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ） 嘅就會用「開通」、「出台」。<br />\n<br />\n用「生效」-- 明報係咪中文拎 F 都可以做記者/編輯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/